headline.main: U.S. Suspends Fast Processing of High-Tech Visa Applications
headline.print_headline: U.S. Suspends Fast Processing of High-Tech Visa Applications

lead_paragraph: Foreigners aiming for temporary jobs at high-tech U.S. companies will undergo a longer visa approval process after the Trump administration announced it will temporarily suspend expedited applications for H-1B visas.
